title: Adesso Home 4046-01 Transitional Two Light Floor Lamp from Stix Collection in Black Finish, Lantern, Canesticks,Beige Paper and Metal
features: Indoor Floor Lantern: Add a warm accent to any space with the Stix floor lantern. The lamp has a sculptural vibe with a twisting frame made up of stacked black cane sticks and black metal poles. Ball feet at the corners elevate the luminaire slightly off the floor.
Functionality: Fabric-like beige paper inside the tower diffuses and softens the light produced by two 60W bulbs. This lamp has a black cord and is smart outlet compatible. Power Source: Plug-In
Home Décor Piece: Elevate your home décor with natural style lighting fixtures from Adesso. Our vast array of lighting options is sure to bring the perfect style and ambience into your home.

Versatile Use: With a compact footprint and elegant design, Adesso Floor Lamps provide a large amount of light in a small amount of space. This functional lamp is ideal for a variety of interior settings including corners, entryways, bedsides, and more.
Product Description: 50 in. height, 60 in. cord length, this floor standing lantern features natural beige paper inner shade and works on 60W incandescent or 13W CFL bulb (not included).
description: Add a warm accent to any space with the Stix floor lantern. The lamp has a sculptural twist, with a twisting frame made up of stacked black cane sticks and black metal poles. Ball feet at the corners elevate the luminaire slightly off the floor. Fabric-like beige paper inside the tower diffuses and softens the light produced by two 60-watt bulbs. This lamp has a black cord and is smart outlet compatible. Bulb is not included. All Adesso lighting products are either UL listed or ETL listed, meaning it has been tested and approved to meet the government-regulated safety standards for the USA.  When shopping for lighting products, we recommend to always look for the UL or ETL marks to ensure you are purchasing lighting that has been tested for safety standards by a 3rd party testing lab. Unfortunately, not all lighting products in the marketplace have been through 3rd party safety testing.Damp/Wet Rating :Dry Rated

The frame of each Stix lamp in this collection is a twisting black metal tower. On either side of each corner a thin vertical cane rod is connected to the frame top and bottom. Thin black cane sticks are stacked and woven on each end to those vertical rods, resulting in the appearance of a stick tower. The share are lined with a fabric-like beige paper. Has ball feet at corners. Foot step switch. Takes 2x60 Watt. 50" Height, 9" Square
